if (params$dataset == "small") {

4 d1 fingerprint

vis_dat(d1)

Each cell is colored according to its type. Yellow for strings, blue for integers, purple for decimals and gray for empty values.

5 Remove ROWS with many missing

Are there rows with many missings?

d1 %>% 
  rowwise() %>% 
  mutate(isna_sum =  sum_isna(c_across(everything()))) %>% 
  mutate(isna_prop = isna_sum / ncol(.))

## #   horovitz_quotient_mm_hg_mit_fi_o2_geschatzt <dbl>,
## #   supportive_o2 <int>, o2_l_min <dbl>, 
na_rowwise <-
  d1 %>% 
  rowwise() %>% 
  mutate(isna_sum =  sum_isna(c_across(everything()))) %>% 
  mutate(isna_prop = isna_sum / ncol(.)) %>% 
  ungroup()
na_rowwise %>% 
  select(id, isna_sum, isna_prop) %>% 
  arrange(-isna_prop) %>% 
  filter(isna_prop > .3)
## # A tibble: 0  3
## #  with 3 variables: id <int>, isna_sum <int>, isna_prop <dbl>

6 Missing data analysis

VIM::aggr(d1)

d1_sumisna <- 
  d1 %>% 
  summarise(across(everything(), sum_isna)) %>% 
  pivot_longer(everything()) %>% 
  mutate(prop = value/nrow(d1)) %>% 
  arrange(-prop) %>% 
  filter(prop > .1)

flog.info("Vars with more than 10% NA to be excluded")

vars_many_missings <- 
  d1 %>% 
  prop_NA %>% 
  pull(name)

8 d2: data without vars with many missings

d2 <-
  d1 %>% 
  select(-all_of(vars_many_missings))

flog.info("Remove vars with many missings (>10%)")

9 Recode dependent variable

d2 <- 
  d2 %>% 
  mutate(verlauf = as.factor(verlauf)) %>% 
  mutate(verlauf = case_when(
    verlauf == 1 ~ "good",
    verlauf == 2 ~ "bad"
  )) 

flog.info("Recoded DV to 'good', 'bad'")
dim(d2)
## [1] 30 70

10 Exclude (near) zero variance (nzv) variables

nzv_vars <- caret::nearZeroVar(d2, names = TRUE)
nzv_vars
## [1] "schwindel"                       "bei_aufnahme_sars_co_v2_positiv"
## [3] "lungenembolie"
d3 <-
  d2 %>% 
  select(-all_of(nzv_vars))

flog.info("Removed near zero variance variables")

11 Excluding attributes

d3 <- labelled::remove_attributes(d3, "spec")

flog.info("Removing attributes 'spec' from df")

13 Writing to disk

if (params$dataset == "small") {
  write_csv(d3, file = here("data", "processed", "data-small-prepared.csv"))
} else {
  write_csv(d3, file = paste0(data_processed_path, "data-prepared.csv"))
}
flog.info("Written 'data-cleaned.csv' to disk.")
